\'ae\'c7u c\'f1a \'aei\'d3m \'aeo l\'c7n 2 ph\'b6i c\'b8ch l\'c7n 1 \'ddt nh\'cat l\'b5 500 mm. Ch\'aanh l\'d6ch gi\'f7a hai l\'c7n \'aeo kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'ad\'eet qu\'b8 3mm. Chu vi ngo\'b5i c\'f1a ti\'d5t di\'d6n \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'ddnh b\'bbng gi
\'b8 tr\'de trung b\'d7nh gi\'f7a hai l\'c7n \'aeo.
