\par }{\b 
\par 
\par 3.6 X\'b8c \'ae\'denh chi\'d2u cao c\'f1a \'ae\'c7u xit\'d0c 
\par }{
\par Tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep \'ae\'c7u xit\'d0c c\'e3 d\'b9ng ch\'e1m c\'c7u ho\'c6c d\'b9ng n\'e3n, chi\'d2u cao f c\'f1a \'ae\'c7u xit\'d0c \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'b8c \'ae\'denh b\'bbng c\'b8ch gi\'e3ng m\'e9t d\'a9y d\'e4i t\'f5 tr\'aan xu\'e8ng d\'ad\'edi v\'b5 \'ae
i\'d2u ch\'d8nh sao cho d\'a9y d\'e4i ti\'d5p x\'f3c v\'edi \'aei\'d3m xa nh\'cat c\'f1a \'ae\'c7u xit\'d0c. D\'efng th\'ad\'edc th\'d0p l\'b8 \'aeo kho\'b6ng c\'b8ch t\'f5 d\'a9y d\'e4i \'ae\'d5n \'aei\'d3m ti\'d5p gi\'b8p gi\'f7a \'ae\'c7u v\'edi ph\'c7
n tr\'f4 c\'f1a xit\'d0c t\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eang sinh th\'cap nh\'cat v\'b5 cao nh\'cat. C\'b8ch \'aeo c\'f4 th\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'ab t\'b6 tr\'aan h\'d7nh 4a \'ae\'e8i v\'edi \'ae\'c7u xit\'d0c d\'b9ng c\'c7u v\'b5 h\'d7nh 4b \'ae\'e8i v\'edi \'ae\'c7
u xit\'d0c d\'b9ng n\'e3n.
\par 
\par 
