i kh\'dd t\'edi \'ae\'e9 ch\'ddnh x\'b8c c\'f1a ph\'d0p \'aeo ch\'d8 n\'aan s\'f6 d\'f4ng xit\'d0c  t\'edi chi\'d2u cao ch\'f8a gi\'edi h\'b9n \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'b8c \'ae\'denh theo c\'abng th\'f8c sau:
