\par \'a7o chi\'d2u cao m\'f8c ch\'cat l\'e1ng sau m\'e7i l\'c7n \'ae\'e6 khi m\'f8c ch\'cat l\'e1ng \'ae\'b7 ho\'b5n to\'b5n \'e6n \'ae\'denh.
